form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: COLOR PHOTOGRAPH SPECIFICATIONS, I-90 SUPPLEMENT FOR ISSUANCE OF I-551

full_text: Screened by NARA, 5/12/2023 I-90 SUPPLEMENT FOR ISSUANCE OF I-551 NOTE: THIS APPLICATION MUST BE SUBMITTED IN PERSON BY THE APPLICANT AT THE NEAREST IMMIGRATION OFFICE OR PORT OF ENTRY TO THE UNITED STATES 70-395-460 ABDi FADUMO DABAR ALIEN NUMBER LAST NAME FIRST NAME MIDDLE NAME I.R.C IN CARE OF ADDRESS 162 Boy(ston street # 50 NUMBER/STREET Boston MA. 02116 CITY STATE ZIP CODE YAREY DABAR SOMALIA MOTHER'S FIRST NAME FATHER'S FIRST NAME CITY/TOWN/VILLAGE OF BIRTH Somaville MA BOSTON BOSTON CITY OF RESIDENCE WHEN CITY OF DESTINATION AT LOCATION OF CONSULATE APPLYING FOR THIS STATUS TIME OF ORIGINAL ADMISSION OR IMMIGRATION OFFICE TO THE UNITED STATES WHERE ADJUSTED 1-01-1907 JFK-NY 12-15-93 SOMALIA DATE OF BIRTH PORT OF ENTRY DATE OF ENTRY COUNTRY OF OR ADJUSTMENT BIRTH NO EYEGLASSES, NO EARRINGS COLOR PHOTOGRAPH MARI SPECIFICATIONS SAMPLE PHOTOGRAPH HEAD SIZE (INCLUDING HAIR) MUST FIT INSIDE OVAL three CHIN SUBMIT THE (3) COLOR PHOTOS MEETING THE FOLLOWING SPECIFICATIONS 22MM (7/8**) HEAD WIDTH PHOTOGRAPH MUST SHOW THE SUBJECT IN A 40 FRONTAL PHOTOGRAPH MUST NOT BE PASTED ON CARDS OR MOUNTED PORTRAIT AS SHOWN ABOVE IN ANY WAY RIGHT EAR MUST BE EXPOSED IN PHOTOGRAPH FOR ALL AP. Two(2) PHOTOGRAPHS OF EVERY APPLICANT, REGARD. PLICANTS, HATS MUST NOT BE WORN LESS OF AGE, MUST BE SUBMITTED PHOTOGRAPH OUTER DIMENSION MUST BE LARGER THAN BUT HEAD SIZE (INCLUDING HAIR) MUST FIT WITHIN PHOTOGRAPHS MUST BE TAKEN WITHIN THIRTY (30) DAYS OF THE ILLUSTRATED OVAL (OUTER DIMENSION DOES NOT INCLUDE APPLICATION DATE BORDER IF ONE IS USED) SNAPSHOTS, GROUP PICTURES, OR FULL LENGTH PORTRAITS PHOTOGRAPH MUST BE COLOR WITH A WHITE BACKGROUND WILL NOT BE ACCEPTED EQUAL IN REFLECTANCE TO BOND TYPING PAPER USING CRAYON OR FELT PEN, TO AVOID MUTILATION OF THE SURFACE OF THE PHOTOGRAPH MUST BE GLOSSY PHOTOGRAPHS, LIGHTLY PRINT YOUR NAME (AND ALIEN REGISTRATION RECEIPT NUMBER IF KNOWN) ON THE BACK OF PHOTOGRAPH MUST NOT BE STAINED, CRACKED, OR MUTI. ALL PHOTOGRAPHS LATED, AND MUST LIE FLAT IMPORTANT NOTE FAILURE TO SUBMIT PHOTOGRAPHS IN PHOTOGRAPHIC IMAGE MUST BE SHARP AND CORRECTLY EX. COMPLIANCE WITH THESE SPECIFICATIONS WILL DELAY THE POSED PHOTOGRAPH MUST BE UN-RETOUCHED PROCESSING OF YOUR APPLICATION ER 530 11-78 (15)
